Deploy sysinfo tool
1. Copy it to a directory than is contained by PATH viariable. For example copy to /user/bin directory.
    sudo cp ./sysinfo /user/bin/
 
2. Set root own the sysinfo file.
    sudo chown root:root /usr/bin/sysinfo
    
3. Change the sysinfo file's permission.
    sudo chmod +x /user/bin/sysinfo
    sudo chmod u+s /user/bin/sysinfo